channel.description:

Please help.
Kingkai

item.title: How do you get onto other people's servers?
item.dc:creator: @Project_Evolution Project Evolution
item.description:
@Project_Evolution wrote:

Well this is… Different. But il try to help.

Go to a webclient, Moparscape, Silabs and make sure the screen loads up and is finished. Now get the Ips of some other peoples server and enter it in the Server Address box. You can actually find that by going into the Advertisement section and looking for servers.
